# Summary
This documentation details the Kochava (Post-install) event streaming integration, which handles events occurring after app installation. It explains how to set up the connection between Amplitude and Kochava to send user identity data and post-install events, with specific focus on the IdentityLink feature that connects user identities with their actions.

